By: Sri Ramana Maharshi
---
Devotee： Why did the Self manifest as this miserable world?

Maharshi： In order that you might seek it. Your eyes cannot see
themselves. Place a mirror before them and they see themselves. Similarly
with the creation.

‘See yourself first and then see the whole world as the Self.’
